
## User Guide (for GitHub Wiki)

# Daily Mood Tracker - User Guide

## Navigation
Today Page:
   Use the slider to select your mood (1-5 scale).
   Optionally type a note about your day.
  -Press Save to store your mood.

-History Page:
   View past moods in a bar or line chart.
   Hover or click on a mood to see the note.
   Filter moods by week or month.

Settings Page:
   Toggle dark mode.
   View your device info (model, OS, etc).

Features
 Mood and note data is saved locally using Ionic Storage.
 Device info is retrieved using @capacitor/device plugin.
 Charts are displayed using Chart.js.

 How to Run
1. Clone the GitHub repository.

